== Temples == * {{ill|Saidaiji (Nara)|ja|西大寺 (奈良市)|qq=draft|qq=draft}} - A temple in {{ill|Nara|ja|奈良県|qq=draft|qq=draft}}, {{ill|Nara City|ja|奈良市|qq=draft|qq=draft}}. The head temple of the {{ill|Shingon Risshu sect|ja|真言律宗|qq=draft|qq=draft}} and one of the {{ill|Seven Great Temples of Nanto|ja|南都七大寺|qq=draft|qq=draft}}. * {{ill|Saidaiji (Okayama)|ja|西大寺 (岡山市)|qq=draft|qq=draft}} - A temple in {{ill|Okayama Prefecture|ja|岡山県|qq=draft|qq=draft}}, {{ill|Okayama City|ja|岡山市|qq=draft|qq=draft}}, {{ill|Higashi-ku, Okayama|ja|東区 (岡山市)|qq=draft|qq=draft}}. A special head temple of the {{ill|Koyasan Shingon-shu|ja|高野山真言宗|qq=draft|qq=draft}}, known for the "{{ill|Eyo (Hadaka Matsuri)|ja|会陽（裸祭）|qq=draft|qq=draft}}." Currently, it includes {{ill|Kannon-in|ja|観音院|qq=draft|qq=draft}} and {{ill|Fumonbo Enman-in|ja|普門坊円満院|qq=draft|qq=draft}}. * {{ill|Saidaiji (Takaoka)|ja|西大寺 (高岡市)|qq=draft|qq=draft}} - A {{ill|Jodo Shinshu Honganji-ha|ja|浄土真宗本願寺派|qq=draft|qq=draft}} temple in {{ill|Takaoka City|ja|高岡市|qq=draft|qq=draft}}, {{ill|Toyama Prefecture|ja|富山県|qq=draft|qq=draft}}. * {{ill|Saidaiji (Higashikushira)|ja|西大寺 (東串良町)|qq=draft|qq=draft}} - A {{ill|Shingon Buddhism|ja|真言宗|qq=draft|qq=draft}} temple in {{ill|Higashikushira Town|ja|東串良町|qq=draft|qq=draft}}, {{ill|Kimotsuki District|ja|肝属郡|qq=draft|qq=draft}}, {{ill|Kagoshima Prefecture|ja|鹿児島県|qq=draft|qq=draft}}. * {{ill|Saiji (Kyoto)|ja|西寺|qq=draft|qq=draft}} - A former temple in {{ill|Kyoto City|ja|京都市|qq=draft|qq=draft}}, also known as {{ill|Saiji|ja|西寺|qq=draft|qq=draft}}.
== Place Names == * Place names in {{ill|Higashi-ku, Okayama|ja|岡山市東区|qq=draft|qq=draft}}: ** {{ill|Saidaiji Area|ja|西大寺地域|qq=draft|qq=draft}} - The jurisdictional area under Okayama City Higashi Ward. Broadly known as Saidaiji, formerly {{ill|Saidaiji City|ja|西大寺市|qq=draft|qq=draft}}. ** {{ill|Saidaiji (School District)|ja|西大寺 (学区)|qq=draft|qq=draft}} - A region within the above area, including the central city area. Narrowly referred to as Saidaiji. ** A large district within the above area. See {{ill|Saidaiji (School District)|ja|西大寺 (学区)|qq=draft|qq=draft}}. * A place name in the {{ill|Fushimi Area (Nara City)|ja|伏見地域|qq=draft|qq=draft}}, {{ill|Nara City|ja|奈良市|qq=draft|qq=draft}}. * {{ill|Saidaiji City|ja|西大寺市|qq=draft|qq=draft}} - A former municipality in Okayama Prefecture. * {{ill|Saidaiji Town|ja|西大寺町|qq=draft|qq=draft}} - A former municipality in Okayama Prefecture. ** {{ill|Saidaiji Town (Disambiguation)|ja|西大寺町 (曖昧さ回避)|qq=draft|qq=draft}} - Disambiguation page. * {{ill|Saidaiji Village|ja|西大寺村|qq=draft|qq=draft}} - Disambiguation page.
== Railways == * {{ill|Saidaiji Station|ja|西大寺駅|qq=draft|qq=draft}} - A station on the {{ill|Ako Line|ja|赤穂線|qq=draft|qq=draft}} of {{ill|JR West|ja|西日本旅客鉄道|qq=draft|qq=draft}}, located in Higashi-ku, Okayama. * {{ill|Yamato-Saidaiji Station|ja|大和西大寺駅|qq=draft|qq=draft}} - A station in Nara City, served by the {{ill|Kintetsu Nara Line|ja|近鉄奈良線|qq=draft|qq=draft}}, {{ill|Kintetsu Kyoto Line|ja|近鉄京都線|qq=draft|qq=draft}}, and {{ill|Kintetsu Kashihara Line|ja|近鉄橿原線|qq=draft|qq=draft}}. * {{ill|Saidaiji-cho/Okayama Art Creation Theater Harenowa-mae Stop|ja|西大寺町・岡山芸術創造劇場ハレノワ前停留場|qq=draft|qq=draft}} - A tram stop on the {{ill|Okayama Electric Tramway Higashiyama Line|ja|岡山電気軌道東山線|qq=draft|qq=draft}} in Kita-ku, Okayama. * {{ill|Shin-Saidaiji-cho-suji Stop|ja|新西大寺町筋停留場|qq=draft|qq=draft}} - A tram stop on the {{ill|Okayama Electric Tramway Seikibashi Line|ja|岡山電気軌道清輝橋線|qq=draft|qq=draft}} in Kita-ku, Okayama. * {{ill|Saidaiji Railway|ja|西大寺鉄道|qq=draft|qq=draft}} - A former railway company in Okayama Prefecture.
== Facilities == * {{ill|Saidaiji Interchange|ja|西大寺インターチェンジ|qq=draft|qq=draft}} - An interchange on the {{ill|Okayama Blue Line|ja|岡山ブルーライン|qq=draft|qq=draft}}, located in Higashi-ku, Okayama. * {{ill|Saidaiji Post Office|ja|西大寺郵便局|qq=draft|qq=draft}} - A post office in Higashi-ku, Okayama. * {{ill|Okayama Prefectural Saidaiji High School|ja|岡山県立西大寺高等学校|qq=draft|qq=draft}} - A high school in Higashi-ku, Okayama.
