== Place Names == * Place names in {{ill|Higashi-ku, Okayama|ja|岡山市東区|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Higashi-ku, Okayama|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki redirects to 東区 (岡山市)}}: ** {{ill|Saidaiji Area|ja|西大寺地域|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Saidaiji Area|qq=}} - The jurisdictional area under Okayama City Higashi Ward. Broadly known as Saidaiji, formerly {{ill|Saidaiji City|ja|西大寺市|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Saidaiji City|qq=}}. ** {{ill|Saidaiji (School District)|ja|西大寺 (学区)|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Saidaiji (School District)|qq=}} - A region within the above area, including the central city area. Narrowly referred to as Saidaiji. ** A large district within the above area. See {{ill|Saidaiji (School District)|ja|西大寺 (学区)|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Saidaiji (School District)|qq=}}. * A place name in the {{ill|Fushimi Area (Nara City)|ja|伏見地域|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Fushimi Area (Nara City)|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}}, [[:en:Nara (city)|Nara City]]. * {{ill|Saidaiji City|ja|西大寺市|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Saidaiji City|qq=}} - A former municipality in Okayama Prefecture. * {{ill|Saidaiji Town|ja|西大寺町|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Saidaiji Town|qq=}} - A former municipality in Okayama Prefecture. ** {{ill|Saidaiji Town (Disambiguation)|ja|西大寺町 (曖昧さ回避)|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Saidaiji Town (Disambiguation)|qq=}} - Disambiguation page. * {{ill|Saidaiji Village|ja|西大寺村|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Saidaiji Village|qq=}} - Disambiguation page.
== Railways == * [[:en:Saidaiji Station|Saidaiji Station]] - A station on the [[:en:Akō Line|Ako Line]] of [[:en:West Japan Railway Company|JR West]], located in Higashi-ku, Okayama. * [[:en:Yamato-Saidaiji Station|Yamato-Saidaiji Station]] - A station in Nara City, served by the [[:en:Nara Line (Kintetsu)|Kintetsu Nara Line]], [[:en:Kyoto Line (Kintetsu)|Kintetsu Kyoto Line]], and [[:en:Kashihara Line|Kintetsu Kashihara Line]]. * {{ill|Saidaiji-cho/Okayama Art Creation Theater Harenowa-mae Stop|ja|西大寺町・岡山芸術創造劇場ハレノワ前停留場|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Saidaiji-cho/Okayama Art Creation Theater Harenowa-mae Stop|qq=}} - A tram stop on the {{ill|Okayama Electric Tramway Higashiyama Line|ja|岡山電気軌道東山線|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Okayama Electric Tramway Higashiyama Line|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki redirects to 岡山電気軌道東山本線}} in Kita-ku, Okayama. * {{ill|Shin-Saidaiji-cho-suji Stop|ja|新西大寺町筋停留場|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Shin-Saidaiji-cho-suji Stop|qq=}} - A tram stop on the [[:en:Seikibashi Line|Okayama Electric Tramway Seikibashi Line]] in Kita-ku, Okayama. * {{ill|Saidaiji Railway|ja|西大寺鉄道|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Saidaiji Railway|qq=}} - A former railway company in Okayama Prefecture.
== Facilities == * {{ill|Saidaiji Interchange|ja|西大寺インターチェンジ|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Saidaiji Interchange|qq=}} - An interchange on the {{ill|Okayama Blue Line|ja|岡山ブルーライン|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Okayama Blue Line|qq=}}, located in Higashi-ku, Okayama. * {{ill|Saidaiji Post Office|ja|西大寺郵便局|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Saidaiji Post Office|qq=}} - A post office in Higashi-ku, Okayama. * {{ill|Okayama Prefectural Saidaiji High School|ja|岡山県立西大寺高等学校|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Okayama Prefectural Saidaiji High School|qq=}} - A high school in Higashi-ku, Okayama.
